>Description:
I'd like to request the addition of a new operation
in DrScheme: save-all-buffers, equivalent to Emacs's
C-x s.  This would be very helpful when working
with a program that's spread over several modules.

(It doesn't necessarily have to have a keybinding;
making the option avaiable on the File menu would be
perfectly fine.)

Thanks!
